config BR2_PACKAGE_GEOGRAPHICLIB
	bool "geographiclib"
	help
	  GeographicLib is a small set of C++ classes for performing
	  conversions between geographic, UTM, UPS, MGRS, geocentric,
	  and local cartesian coordinates, for gravity (e.g.,
	  EGM2008), geoid height, and geomagnetic field (e.g.,
	  WMM2020) calculations, and for solving geodesic
	  problems. (The library may be used from .NET applications
	  using the NETGeographicLib wrapper library.) It is a
	  suitable replacement for the core functionality provided by
	  geotrans. The library is licensed under the MIT/X11 License;
	  see LICENSE.txt for the terms.

	  https://geographiclib.sourceforge.io/

